        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>clear lumber [300012814], lumber by quality [300012813], lumber [300012785], wood by product [300012779], wood and wood by product [300011913], plant material [300124117], biological material [300265629], materials by origin [300206573], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
